title: Pocket Guild v1.08 full
description:
Light-hearted MMO simulator!

Pocket Guild is a single player game that puts
you in charge of your own fantasy MMO guild.

Recruit members, take down bosses,
and lead your guild to glory!

Features:
- Choose your character
- Create / manage your guild members
- Obtain legendary characters
- Over 260 unique hand crafted characters!
- Plan/run through unique dungeons
- Entertaining, hand crafted bosses
- Loot, ninjas, guild drama.. and more!
